Title: 6.14. Adding lists
import operator
 >>> list1 = [1,0]
 >>> list2 = [1,2]
 >>> list3 = list1 + list2
 >>> list3
 [1, 0, 1, 2]
Ok, that is one way, here is another:
 >>> list3 = map(operator.add, list1,list2)
 >>> list3
 [2, 2]
